FBIS3-15778 "drsov047_m_94006" FBIS-SOV-94-047 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Mar 1994 Tajikistan Russian Border Guards Detain Three `Armed Men' LD1003145794 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1149 GMT 10 Mar 94 LD1003145794 Moscow INTERFAX Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] According to the press bureau of the Russian border guards, on Wednesday three armed men were detained crossing the Tajik-Afghan border from Afghanistan at the Khorog border unit. During the operation Russian border guards came under gun fire from three points in the Afghan territory. They retaliated. One of the gunmen was wounded. None of the border guards was hurt.
